## Directory Rules

### Never Modify These Directories

- **`tmp/`** - Temporary files (cache, pids, sockets)
- **`log/`** - Application logs
- **`public/assets/`** - Compiled assets (generated automatically)
- **`db/schema.rb`** - Database schema (generated from migrations)

### App Directory Organization

#### Controllers (`app/controllers/`)

```
controllers/
├── concerns/
│   ├── authenticatable.rb     # Shared authentication logic
│   └── authorizable.rb         # Shared authorization logic
├── application_controller.rb
├── articles_controller.rb
├── comments_controller.rb
└── sessions_controller.rb
```

**Rules:**
- One controller per resource
- Use concerns for shared logic
- Keep controllers thin (<10 lines per action)

#### Models (`app/models/`)

```
models/
├── concerns/
│   ├── publishable.rb         # Shared publishing logic
│   ├── searchable.rb          # Shared search logic
│   └── sluggable.rb           # Shared slug generation
├── application_record.rb
├── current.rb                 # Rails 8 authentication
├── user.rb
├── article.rb
├── comment.rb
└── session.rb
```

**Rules:**
- One model per database table
- Use concerns for shared behavior
- Keep models focused (single responsibility)

#### Views (`app/views/`)

```
views/
├── layouts/
│   ├── application.html.erb   # Main layout
│   ├── admin.html.erb          # Admin layout
│   └── mailer.html.erb         # Email layout
├── shared/
│   ├── _header.html.erb
│   ├── _footer.html.erb
│   ├── _navigation.html.erb
│   └── _flash.html.erb
├── articles/
│   ├── index.html.erb
│   ├── show.html.erb
│   ├── new.html.erb
│   ├── edit.html.erb
│   ├── _form.html.erb          # Form partial
│   └── _article.html.erb       # Display partial
└── comments/
    ├── _comment.html.erb
    └── _form.html.erb
```

**Rules:**
- Organize by resource (plural names)
- Use `shared/` for cross-resource partials
- Partials start with underscore
- Form partials named `_form.html.erb`

#### JavaScript (`app/javascript/`)

```
javascript/
├── controllers/               # Stimulus controllers
│   ├── application.js
│   ├── dropdown_controller.js
│   ├── modal_controller.js
│   ├── autosave_controller.js
│   └── flash_controller.js
└── application.js             # Entry point
```

**Rules:**
- One Stimulus controller per behavior
- Name with `_controller.js` suffix
- Keep controllers under 200 lines

#### Assets (`app/assets/`)

```
assets/
├── stylesheets/
│   └── application.tailwind.css  # Main stylesheet
└── images/
    ├── logo.png
    ├── hero.jpg
    └── icons/
        ├── edit.svg
        └── delete.svg
```

**Rules:**
- Use Propshaft for asset management
- Keep images organized in subdirectories
- Prefer SVG for icons

#### Jobs (`app/jobs/`)

```
jobs/
├── application_job.rb
├── article_notification_job.rb
├── data_export_job.rb
└── cache_refresh_job.rb
```

**Rules:**
- One job per background task
- Name with `_job.rb` suffix
- Keep jobs focused (single responsibility)

#### Channels (`app/channels/`)

```
channels/
├── application_cable/
│   ├── channel.rb
│   └── connection.rb
├── comments_channel.rb
└── notifications_channel.rb
```

**Rules:**
- One channel per real-time feature
- Name with `_channel.rb` suffix

